title: Songsarni maya thiliao
lyrics:
Songsarni maya thiliao
Bese gwbao gelebaonw nwng -2
(A)
Songsarni lamayao dathabai nwng lwgw
Andailangwn nwng be songsarao
Ha . . . . . . . .Ha . . . . . . . .
Dorseni mwjangkhou mwjang dasan nwng lwgw
Khwmsi songsarni saglwbnayao  - 2
(B)
Khristo Jisuni khebnwini fwifinnaya
Swrgwmbwgou honwi be songsarao
Ho . . . . . . . .Ho . . . . . . . .
Thamtim jananwi thadw nwngswrw lwgw
Swrgw raijwni lama lanw  -  2
